reviews.comments:
Warm host (only Spanish speaking - we are italian and had problems to communicate);
Her apt is as it appears in pictures; really hot during summer : air conditioning needed);
Quiet neighborhood and apt close to two metro stops (different lines);
 2 toilet paper rolls and one towel each were provided for 3 guests;
We didn't use kitchen so no news about that;
Small bathroom, water flushes on the floor when you have shower;
No ornaments or decorations in the apt.
